Saving_Private_Ryan_poster.jpg&h=fe6817fa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/8/81/Inglourious_Basterds_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F8%2F81%2FInglourious_Basterds_Poster.jpg&h=90efad21&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/f/f9/Edge_of_Tomorrow_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Ff%2Ff9%2FEdge_of_Tomorrow_Poster.jpg&h=59f90ddf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.描述諾曼第登陸後，雷恩家4名於前線參戰的兒子中，3個兒子皆已於兩週內於海外各戰區陸續陣亡，其母親將在一天內接到三個兒子的死訊。而隸屬101空降師二等兵的小兒子詹姆斯&middot;法蘭西斯&middot;雷恩則在參與諾曼地的空降行動後下落不明，美國陸軍參謀長馬歇爾上將得知此事後出於人道考量，特令在法國前線作戰的美國陸軍遊騎兵組織一支8人小隊深入敵後，只為在人海茫茫、槍林彈雨中找出生死未卜的二等兵雷恩<br />\n<br />\n2.在二次大戰期間德占區的法國，外號「猶太獵人」（The Jew Hunter）的親衛隊上校漢斯&middot;蘭達（Hans Landa，克里斯多夫&middot;華茲飾）在一位法國奶農皮埃爾&middot;拉帕提（Perrier LaPadite）的家中審問他。拉帕提為了家人的安全供認了猶太裔的德瑞芙斯（Dreyfus）一家就藏在他家的地板下。蘭達讓親衛隊士兵隔著地板掃射殺害了這一家人，但少女蘇珊娜（Shosanna，梅蘭妮&middot;羅蘭飾）僥倖逃脫<br />\n<br />\n3.外星生物「擬態」（Mimics）入侵地球，人類組成地球聯合防衛部節節敗退後，美國少校威廉‧凱吉（William Cage）負責地球防衛部的公關代言，前往英國前線宣傳，指揮官布里干（Brigham）將軍任命凱吉登陸歐洲，拍攝戰場進行公關宣傳。凱吉驚恐拒絕，於是將軍以逃兵身份將凱吉空運到倫敦基地，凱吉被迫參戰，瀕死之際被外星生物的藍色血液淋到。死亡後，凱吉自動回到參戰前一天<br />\n<br />\n8 30PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=2%2FmELneL9Q%2Bp6j2sEUyr0%2FrdRd5YSNtYq48oyOX%2FX2w%3D&h=b408c5d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=2%2FmELneL9Q%2Bp6j2sEUyr0%2FrdRd5YSNtYq48oyOX%2FX2w%3D&h=0231bf6a\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3e53e1fca280fae02b102b9dce4567901213750","tid":2182596,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T12:00:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9aeea5e79c240a65dedb93853dec89d3fd00905","tid":2182596,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T12:42:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9fcd4df12a055ce2c30862681d116f726650468","tid":2182596,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T14:52:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8f15e0a86153807f8edb3cdfe7da8c42a2aba6f","tid":2182596,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T15:32:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7febcf2d88e470d9ed06f67fee5a1afcc7b6f5e9","tid":2182596,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T17:24:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2020816103b70b473021fbdbc7cdf621d0dd6a5","tid":2182596,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T19:29:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}